Process called "time_span_allocate" returns Integer:
    @Reasoning
    Reserves a fresh Duration-shaped TimeSpan buffer. Delegates to
    duration_allocate. Distinct from the bounded-interval TimeSpan struct
    accessed via time_span_create.
    @End Reasoning
    @Implementation
    Direct delegation.
    @End Implementation
    @Performance_Hints
    Single tier-3 alloc.
    @End Performance_Hints
    @Security_Scope
    Caller must release via time_span_free.
    @End Security_Scope
    Return proc duration_allocate from DurationModule
End Process

